Body: Description: Hi i have noticed a few devices with very old Last Seen Times, while remoting to these devices i notice that EPP is installed but nor running, i am unable to uninstall as the options are not there and install gives me the error shared in the image.
What We've Learned Updated: 30-05 Customer encounter an issue with uninstalling the client  so we schedule a remote session to assist them
Next Steps Updated: 30-05 Waiting for customer to confirm that we can close the case.
